    <questiontext format="markdown">
      <text>**31.1 E4 Natural Spline**

Find the natural cubic spline which interpolates the data

{@T@}

\\\(s_1(x), x\in[x_1,x_2]=\\\) [[input:S_s1]] [[validation:S_s1]]
 
\\\(s_2(x), x\in[x_2,x_3]=\\\) [[input:S_s2]] [[validation:S_s2]] 

\\\(s_3(x), x\in[x_3,x_4]=\\\) [[input:S_s3]] [[validation:S_s3]]
 
[[feedback:s1]]</text>
    </questiontext>
